@startuml KorusLedger_Architecture

!theme materia-outline

skinparam componentStyle rectangle



package "Client Layer" {

    [Mobile/Web App] as Client

}



node "Infrastructure" {

    database "PostgreSQL" as DB

    queue "RabbitMQ" as Broker

    folder "Shared Storage (Volume)" as Storage

}



package "Backend Services" {

    [KorusCore (Kotlin)] <<Orchestrator>> as Core

    [OCR-Worker (Rust)] <<Processor>> as Worker

}



Client --> Core : 1. Upload Ticket (REST)

Core --> Storage : 2. Save File

Core --> DB : 3. Create Record (PENDING)

Core --> Broker : 4. Dispatch Job (JSON)



Broker --> Worker : 5. Pull Task

Worker --> Storage : 6. Read File

Worker --> DB : 7. Update OCR Data (COMPLETED)



@enduml